目前只有Linux版本

編譯需求：
	Loki:
		http://loki-lib.sourceforge.net/
	Qt >= 4.2:
		http://www.qtsoftware.com/products
	Boost C++ Libraries with Regex:
		http://www.boost.org/
	FFMpeg Libraries after 2008:
		http://www.ffmpeg.org/
On Debian-based system:
	# apt-get install libloki-dev libqt4-dev libboost-regex-dev libavcodec-dev libavformat-dev

編譯步驟：
	$ qmake
	$ make

